The xf86-input-wacom driver is the wacom-specific X11 input driver for the X.Org X Server version 1.7 and later (X11R7.5 or later).
The following distributions ship xf86-input-wacom:
* Arch Linux
* Debian Squeeze and later
* Fedora 12 and later
* Gentoo
* OpenSuse 10.3 and later
* Ubuntu 10.04 and later

